OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1776272750
OL,3,CMayor backs campaign for Birmingham
OL,4,CBalti to be given UNESCO protected
OL,5,Cstatus
OL,7,FSelf-confessed balti fan and Mayor of
OL,8,Fthe West Midlands, Richard Parker, has
OL,9,Fthrown his weight behind a new
OL,10,Fcampaign for the Birmingham Balti to
OL,11,Fbe given Unesco protected status.
OL,13,FThe signature dish - which originated
OL,14,Fin the city in 1975 - is a type of
OL,15,Fcurry, cooked and served in a thin,
OL,16,Fpressed-steel wok over a high flame,
OL,17,Fusing vegetable oil instead of ghee.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1776272750
OL,3,CMayor backs campaign for Birmingham
OL,4,CBalti to be given UNESCO protected
OL,5,Cstatus
OL,7,FUnesco's Intangible Cultural Heritage
OL,8,Fstatus would help preserve the cooking
OL,9,Ftechniques, as well as recognising the
OL,10,Frole the balti has played in the
OL,11,Farea's cultural heritage.
OL,13,FMr Parker told ITV News Central he had
OL,14,Ffirst fallen in love with the dish
OL,15,Fwhen he moved to the city four decades
OL,16,Fago.
OL,18,F"I've lived in Birmingham for over 40
OL,19,Fyears now - I spent my early years
OL,20,Fyear experiencing the fantastic food,
OL,21,Fwhich I really enjoyed," he said.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1776272750
OL,3,CMayor backs campaign for Birmingham
OL,4,CBalti to be given UNESCO protected
OL,5,Cstatus
OL,7,F"And I really support the case for
OL,8,FUnesco status, and the work being
OL,9,Fdone, to secure that for the balti
OL,10,Fdish, and also the Balti Triangle in
OL,11,FBirmingham."
OL,13,FThe campaign was launched this month,
OL,14,Fled by a group of restaurateurs from
OL,15,FBirmingham's famous Balti Triangle -
OL,16,Fthe area around Ladypool Road, Stoney
OL,17,FLane, and Stratford Road in Sparkbrook
OL,18,Fand Sparkhill.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1776272750
OL,3,CMayor backs campaign for Birmingham
OL,4,CBalti to be given UNESCO protected
OL,5,Cstatus
OL,7,FAmong them is Zafar Hussain, from
OL,8,FShababs, who said he believed having
OL,9,Fthe status would be a boost for
OL,10,Fbusiness - as well as helping to root
OL,11,Fout poor imitations.
OL,13,F"We have people visiting Birmingham
OL,14,Fand coming for about you to sample a
OL,15,Fbounty here in the Balti Triangle from
OL,16,Fall over the world," he said.
OL,18,F"Other people don't cook it using the
OL,19,Fsame method, not in the traditional
OL,20,Fway. We want to make sure people know
OL,21,Fwhat a true balti is."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
