OL,3,CMayor backs campaign for Birmingham
OL,4,CBalti to be given UNESCO protected
OL,5,Cstatus
OL,7,FOther food and drinks to have been
OL,8,Fgiven the status in the past include
OL,9,FBelgian beer, Neapolitan pizza, and
OL,10,Fthe French baguette.
